{"tid":1027450,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"打麻雀叻是否無用?","createTime":"2019-02-18T22:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T05:05:55.000Z","uid":54930,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"21b002032231694b698b4a9ede9728092223e29c","tid":1027450,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T22:44:48.000Z","msg":"事緣一次我係咁贏到個朋友無晒癮，令我諗自己打麻雀叻可以有咩用?<br />\n如果為左大家開心，我特登放水，又無意思<br />\n但唔計錢，又唔好玩<br />\n就算計錢，贏返來既又只係自己朋友錢，唔同賭波賭馬，可以贏街外錢<br />\n而平時又唔可以拎出黎威，問你有咩叻，一個大男人又唔可以話自己打麻雀勁<br />\n又唔似人地運動員，可以去比賽<br />\n<br />\n以前好proud of自己打得勁，而家諗諗下發覺冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17f7f7166830ea2c29c8f810aefb1a6590cf7a3","tid":1027450,"uid":56782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T22:47:31.000Z","msg":"去雀館 / \t網上"},{"pid":"49f612cd50ccd279e174e0c6e610cee5e1a3b041","tid":1027450,"uid":109759,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T22:48:02.000Z","msg":"有麻雀館<br />\n你去到就知自己有幾廢"},{"pid":"7f17b45527077a8ab026b7617182654c482d9d4d","tid":1027450,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"49f612cd50ccd279e174e0c6e610cee5e1a3b041","tid":1027450,"uid":109759,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T22:48:02.000Z","msg":"有麻雀館<br />\n你去到就知自己有幾廢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T22:49:07.000Z","msg":"要比人抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9eb962b56e154ef3a756b1879a8ea55377658c","tid":1027450,"uid":29048,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7f17b45527077a8ab026b7617182654c482d9d4d","tid":1027450,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"49f612cd50ccd279e174e0c6e610cee5e1a3b041","tid":1027450,"uid":109759,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T22:48:02.000Z","msg":"有麻雀館<br />\n你去到就知自己有幾廢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T22:49:07.000Z","msg":"要比人抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB