783e1a68","tid":1027450,"uid":183358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:34:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事緣一次我係咁贏到個朋友無晒癮，令我諗自己打麻雀叻可以有咩用?<br />\n如果為左大家開心，我特登放水，又無意思<br />\n但唔計錢，又唔好玩<br />\n就算計錢，贏返來既又只係自己朋友錢，唔同賭波賭馬，可以贏街外錢<br />\n而平時又唔可以拎出黎威，問你有咩叻，一個大男人又唔可以話自己打麻雀勁<br />\n又唔似人地運動員，可以去比賽<br />\n<br />\n以前好proud of自己打得勁，而家諗諗下發覺冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁樣只係你自己好運， 完全唔關技術是打麻雀主要都係靠運氣， 半年前打牌試過冧足12舖莊， 食埋么九，大三元，十八羅漢嗰啲奇牌， 直到依家打牌未贏過。 正所謂人有三衰六旺，呢排你行運啫，唔代表你打牌勁， 如果你又真係覺得自己咁旺嘅不妨去澳門賭一賭。"},{"pid":"79ead51f40b3751c1c2fca2919ee2932943d2de7","tid":1027450,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"同啲再勁啲嘅朋友打囉，如果真係鍾意嘅話，再喺出面識啲勁人打囉，不過小心天仙局就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6212798fd8a70fa0cb6c4469295340dd003e0773","tid":1027450,"uid":201992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:20:18.000Z","msg":"報呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7PnJ3V5l614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7PnJ3V5l614&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=fa19e223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7PnJ3V5l614</a>"},{"pid":"8db1163fc87f40849a1ed8e55620edc9bd23ac48","tid":1027450,"uid":43046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6212798fd8a70fa0cb6c4469295340dd003e0773","tid":1027450,"uid":201992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:20:18.000Z","msg":"報呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7PnJ3V5l614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7PnJ3V5l614&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=fa19e223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7PnJ3V5l614</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"屌你琴晚我先睇完<br />\nYoutube推薦"},{"pid":"a0cdfb3da015b279863d268bc9ad309498a11027","tid":1027450,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,